
ABOUT THE TOOL
--------------
This patch helps in adding BadgerTrap on top of Linux Kernel. This program
helps in instrumenting the kernel to intercept TLB misses for programs on 
the fly in order to infer behaviour of TLB misses.

COPYRIGHT
---------
The copyright for this software is held by Mark D. Hill, Michael M. Swift and David A. Wood
from University of Wisconsin - Madison.

